France Lends $48 Million to Jordan Water Project, Al Ghad Says

-- B y   M o h a m m a d   T a y s e e r
-- 
2011-07-04T10:59:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-04/france-lends-48-million-to-jordan-water-project-al-ghad-says.html
The French government aid agency
loaned $48 million to help fund a drinking water project in
 Jordan ,  Al Ghad  newspaper said.  The money is part of a $100 million loan pledged in 2009 by
the Agence Francaise de Developpement to exploit the Disi
aquifer to supply the capital Amman and other regions with
drinking water, the newspaper said, citing an identified
official.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mohammad Tayseer via Dubait ; or
Nayla Razzouk in Amman at 
 Nrazzouk2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss at 
 sev@bloomberg.net  